// products.js
const products = [
    {
      id: 1,
      name: "Product 1",
      price: "100 INR",
      description: "This is a detailed description of Product 1.",
      terms: "Terms and conditions for Product 1.",
      images: [
        "data:image/jpeg;base64,",
        "data:image/jpeg;base64,",
        "data:image/jpeg;base64,",
      ],
      specifications: ["Feature 1", "Feature 2", "Feature 3"],
      reviews: [
        { user: "Alice", comment: "Great product!", rating: 5 },
        { user: "Bob", comment: "Good value for money.", rating: 4 },
      ],
    },
    {
      id: 2,
      name: "Product 2",
      price: "200 INR",
      description: "This is a detailed description of Product 2.",
      terms: "Terms and conditions for Product 2.",
      images: [
        "https://via.placeholder.com/300?text=Product+2+Image+1",
        "https://via.placeholder.com/300?text=Product+2+Image+2",
      ],
      specifications: ["High-quality material", "Long battery life", "Compact design"],
      reviews: [
        { user: "Chris", comment: "Looks great!", rating: 4 },
      ],
    },
    // Add more products
  ];
  
  export default products;
